# YC Idea Grader — environment
#
# This tool runs on your LOCAL Claude Code subscription via the Claude Agent SDK.
# There is NO API key. Do not set ANTHROPIC_API_KEY — the server refuses to start
# if one is present (a stray key would silently bill the paid API instead of your
# subscription).
#
# Optional: override the model. Defaults to claude-opus-4-8 (1M context).
# GRADER_MODEL=claude-sonnet-4-6

# Optional: override the server port (default 8787).
# PORT=8787
